title: ETH v1 Listing: Add SAND market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list SAND on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: Scale C.R.E.A.M.’s coverage of GameFi markets.

For:
Add SAND market with Collateral Factor: 45% and Collateral Cap: $1M

Against:
Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
